snippet: Fifth-seeded Dominic Thiem of Austria reached his second quarterfinals of the young season when he defeated qualifier Gastao Elias of Portugal 3-6, 7-6 (7), 6-3 in the Argentina Open on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Fifth-seeded Dominic Thiem of Austria reached his second quarterfinals of the young season when he defeated qualifier Gastao Elias of Portugal 3-6, 7-6 (7), 6-3 in the Argentina Open on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Thiem, Almagro Into Quarterfinals in Argentina
headline.main: Thiem, Almagro Into Quarterfinals in Argentina
